OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIsolated outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fclearing the south coast early Sunday.
OL,7,FOtherwise, a largely dry and fine day
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells developing. Feeling
OL,9,Fcooler than Saturday with a freshening
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright and sunny evening,
OL,13,Fwith largely clear skies developing
OL,14,Fovernight. Winds easing, allowing
OL,15,Ftemperatures to dip low enough for a
OL,16,Ftouch of frost in some prone rural
OL,17,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
