OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAfter a chilly but sunny
OL,6,Fstart, cloud will build from the north
OL,7,Fwith patchy rain possible by midday.
OL,8,FThe rain fragmenting as it progresses,
OL,9,Fwith some parts perhaps staying dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FRemaining changeable on Tuesday with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of patchy rain clearing
OL,14,Fsouth. Turning blustery with sunny
OL,15,Fspells and heavy showers both
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday. Feeling
OL,17,Fchilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
